  "detailed_description": "Roll your cube to get to the goal, but think before rolling!  Sometimes you need to stand on a switch to raise a drawbridge and reach the goal, as seen below.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1505010/extras/2e07accc66f6d2138b024a2935f3bd1c.poster.avif?t=1650920885\" width=292 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1505010/extras/2e07accc66f6d2138b024a2935f3bd1c.webm?t=1650920885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1505010/extras/2e07accc66f6d2138b024a2935f3bd1c.mp4?t=1650920885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In some levels you can morph into a different shape that lets you move exactly one tile at a time, but at the cost of not being able to stand up. In this mode, the only way you can change orientation is by moving across a bridge.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1505010/extras/671219e42a64fbfc46f2798aab7136f9.poster.avif?t=1650920885\" width=292 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1505010/extras/671219e42a64fbfc46f2798aab7136f9.webm?t=1650920885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1505010/extras/671219e42a64fbfc46f2798aab7136f9.mp4?t=1650920885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can also move your player from one side of the tile to the other, perhaps by traversing a Mobiüs strip.  It's a topologist's dream!  (or nightmare)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1505010/extras/6f0fc4018f5b20dedfa0c4bdb3bdee42.avif?t=1650920885\" width=464 height=220 /></span>",
